{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/zh-TW/the-beginning","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"350d903b-32ea-513a-82a5-bea56171e133","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 780px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/64331401d5b5d4fc5afe54ac47bc8248/be796/the-beginning.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.75000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/64331401d5b5d4fc5afe54ac47bc8248/8ac56/the-beginning.webp 240w,\n/static/64331401d5b5d4fc5afe54ac47bc8248/d3be9/the-beginning.webp 480w,\n/static/64331401d5b5d4fc5afe54ac47bc8248/8369b/the-beginning.webp 780w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/64331401d5b5d4fc5afe54ac47bc8248/09b79/the-beginning.jpg 240w,\n/static/64331401d5b5d4fc5afe54ac47bc8248/7cc5e/the-beginning.jpg 480w,\n/static/64331401d5b5d4fc5afe54ac47bc8248/be796/the-beginning.jpg 780w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/64331401d5b5d4fc5afe54ac47bc8248/be796/the-beginning.jpg\"\n          alt=\"alt text\"\n          title=\"The Beginning\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n當我決定要架這個網站的時候，腦中馬上就浮現一個問題需要答案： 我要寫什麼？特別是在擁有不同社群軟體的情況下，如果可以把這裡跟他們有所區別就太好了。我檢視了自己在不同社群軟體上的使用行為，發現有很大的差別。</p>\n<h3 id=\"facebook\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#facebook\" aria-label=\"facebook permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Facebook</h3>\n<p>我基本上都在潛水，幾乎不會發文。有的時候會分享其他人的文章。</p>\n<h3 id=\"instagram\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#instagram\" aria-label=\"instagram permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Instagram</h3>\n<p>我的最愛。這是我最常使用的平台，會在上面分享我的生活點滴，並且每天與我的朋友們互動。</p>\n<h3 id=\"twitter\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#twitter\" aria-label=\"twitter permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Twitter</h3>\n<p>我用來追蹤我關心的議題與人物。Twitter通常都會有第一手的消息。</p>\n<p>未來我會分享：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>科技/程式</li>\n<li>投資相關議題</li>\n<li>各種書籍讀後感</li>\n<li>學習筆記（吉他/日文）</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/zh-TW/the-beginning","tagSlugs":["/tag/personal/","/tag/random/"],"langKey":"zh-TW"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-08-08","description":"我會寫些什麼呢？","tags":["Personal","Random"],"title":"起點","socialImage":"/the-beginning.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/zh-TW/the-beginning","translations":["zh-TW"]}},"staticQueryHashes":["3016035026","3475168723","4282317205"]}